T*
() Tj
T*
(Capacity Snapshot \(Current Policy\)) Tj
T*
(With 3,500,000 vB block budget and 120s block time:) Tj
T*
(- 1 in / 2 out \(~566 vB\) -> ~51.5 TPS) Tj
T*
(- 2 in / 2 out \(~615 vB\) -> ~47.4 TPS) Tj
T*
(- 3 in / 2 out \(~664 vB\) -> ~43.9 TPS) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(This is why tx-shape distribution directly drives sustained throughput.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
