T*
(Purpose: deterministic acceptance rules and consistent mempool/block behavior.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Components:) Tj
T*
(- Transaction verification with parallel workers.) Tj
T*
(- Optional C UTXO batch checker for fast LMDB existence checks.) Tj
T*
(- Block verification and consensus admission gates.) Tj
T*
(- BPoW bond/stake state machines \(bond.lmdb, stake.lmdb\) and fee-pool routing logic.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(BPoW execution in this layer:) Tj
T*
(- validates miner proof fields in block body \(miner_pubkey, reward_address, miner_signature\),) Tj
T*
(- derives expected bond identity from raw pubkey + role domain,) Tj
T*
(- enforces bond state/confirmations/threshold at active heights,) Tj
T*
(- classifies slashable-invalid vs stale/orphan conditions deterministically.) Tj
T*
